<paragraph id="IFRS17_B73" base="F55667404"><paranum>B73</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="B73"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P0758">To determine the discount rates at the date of initial recognition of a <xref base="F55666942" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0526">group of contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0159"/></ph></xref> described in <xref id="IFRS17_X0632" base="F59236365" href="IFRS17_gB72-B85.dita#IFRS17_gB72-B85/IFRS17_gB72-B85_TI">paragraphs B72(b)&#x2013;B72(e)</xref>, an entity may use weighted-average discount rates over the period that contracts in the group are issued, which applying <xref id="IFRS17_X0633" base="F59236366" href="IFRS17_22.dita#IFRS17_22">paragraph 22</xref> cannot exceed one year.</p></body></paragraph>